<DOCNO> LA110794-0053 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 096171 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 7, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 3; Column 1; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
