<TEXT>
<P>
 Dominic J. Saccacio has been named chairman and chief executive of Datatape 
Inc., a Pasadena-based manufacturer of high-performance tape record systems. 
Saccacio succeeds Gordon Smith, who left Datatape after it was taken over in 
August by Delta Tango of Santa Barbara. Saccacio, who joined Datatape at that 
time, formerly headed his own consulting firm. 
